Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Number 18684, Sister Krone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We hereby appoint you\Nto be Mom for Plant Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was a sudden opening\Nat Plant Four for a Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been recommending you for some time,\Nwhich is why you were selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been recommending me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma is at the gate to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pack up immediately\Nand go back to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye. Please do your best\Nat the new plant, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You don't look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, this is an honor. I'll get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That woman. She intends to get rid of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all or nothing, but I have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let everything go her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Krone! The food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Krone? Wasn't she with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is she in her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. She has some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should start eating first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Krone's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom said she has work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to the facts on this note,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the other perfect scorers know about\Nthe secret and are trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the two high-quality ones below them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have evidence regarding their escape,\Nbut please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave this alone,\Nit'll get dangerous! At this rate—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they are being kept under control, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they are kept under control,\Nthen there are no issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how it was back in my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is troublesome, Sister Krone,\Nthat you get in Isabella's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isabella and her plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isabella is a necessary pawn for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are insufficient to take her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will become troublesome for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May we offer the best plate at the Tifari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May the farm have maximum profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were in it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no chance of winning\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You brats better escape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're good at playing tag, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and run...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then destroy this damned world we live in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you, that was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start switching out the chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go over the plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Norman and Emma will climb the wall\Nto inspect the vicinity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don and Gilda, stay outside where you can see\Nthe south window on the House's second floor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just in case I fail to distract Mom,\NI'll signal you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let Emma and Norman know\Nto cancel the inspection immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please let this go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I eliminated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I eliminated Sister Krone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I didn't need her anymore.\NThat's why I eliminated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our deal is over, right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I fired as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You need me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to use me\Nso you can control them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,indirectly and peacefully\Nfrom behind the scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing a good job. To you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:12:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you were a useful dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I kept you by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're a lying traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there shouldn't be a problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's true that there is no fault with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is an unfair dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's also unfortunate for me.\NThis was unforeseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to let you go until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll control them by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ray. Please forgive me\Nfor the things I'm about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there for a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you out when I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. From the speed of the two signals\Nrunning through the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it must be Emma and Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading straight for the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's for inspection?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I don't care about the chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you'll protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For their sake, you won't get me killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why if you wanted to suppress me,\Nyou'll definitely use a different method.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Ray.\NThank you for all your hard work until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully things go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray hasn't signaled us, but Mom came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gilda, you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check inside the House!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray? Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gilda, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is inspection canceled?\NAre we stopping Emma and Norman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're enforcing the inspection!\NWe have to stop Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is now our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to let them inspect no matter what,\Nbefore Mom gets to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've been living together for ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the first time\Ntalking to you without the acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Emma.\NNice to meet you, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, please be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to pretend to be good kids\Nwho don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's just the caretaker\Nand the children meant to be food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But please don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I adore you. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you as if you were my own children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I'm here.\NI want you to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give up what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give up resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you, I don't want you to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to have to make you all suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a happy life, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A warm home\Nfilled with love and delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing hunger, coldness, or the truth,\Nyou can die with a satisfied feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What part of that is unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A happy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the happiness you speak of\Nsimilar to the end that Conny met?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death happens in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until that moment,\NConny lived a rich life full of smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any fake smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I suffer, I will live freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will decide for myself what happiness is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous outside, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Let's all live together\Nhappily inside our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until the end, when your time runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want the five of you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five? Not three?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll quit being a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt. It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You poor thing. My adorable Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's why I said to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But you haven't hugged me in a while,\Nso that made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Norman, you realized it too.\NThat's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'll control you until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how special you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A special meal\Nthat only a special One can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The highest quality children that I have raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have to protect you.\NNo matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had to do this\Nbecause you weren't going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, what happened to Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did she get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't move for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can welcome tomorrow safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay put and celebrate, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got a notice from the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your shipment date has been set.
